review.name: Just got to love Janet.
review.reviewBody: Excellent compilation of Janet's talent. I love her vision and how she brings so much emotion to video. If you are a fan of Janet, you will enjoy the Design. I was also amazed at the supporting cast. Jennifer Lopez, Paula Abdul, etc., also talented and beautiful women. Janet surrounds herself with talent, which elevates them and shows us how gracious she is in enhancing others also. I have always enjoyed her music. But her videos were always something to look forward to seeing. She has shown us fun, sexy, passion & pain in video. She has proved that she is definitely one of the most talented and beautiful women of color of our century.
